Resource Profile: SehatukCore Medication Request

Official URL: https://www.sehatuk.ae/uae-fhir/r4/StructureDefinition/medication-request Version: 1.0.0
Active as of 2022-11-19 Computable Name: SehatukCoreMedicationRequest

SehatukCore constraints on MedicationRequest resource mandating support for elements relevant to the prescriptions being requested on a prior authorization request

Usage:

  • This Resource Profile is not used by any profiles in this Implementation Guide
